Indian Ocean (Parin &amp; Abramov 1986b; 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9A73DF6E624066FC695A6D13999982" box="[998,1172,1655,1680]" pageId="15" pageNumber="276" refId="ref17192" refString="Abramov, A. A. (1992) Species composition and distribution of Epigonus (Epigonidae) in the world ocean. Journal of Ichthyology, 32, 94 - 108." type="journal article">Abramov 1992</bibRefCitation>
