<bibRefCitation id="EF9A73DF6E624066FE3C5A86156399A6" box="[435,622,1692,1717]" pageId="15" pageNumber="276" refId="ref20459" refString="Mochizuki, K. (1990) Apogonidae. In: Amaoka, K., Matsuura, K., Inada, T., Takeda, M., Hatanaka, H. &amp; Okada, K. (Eds.), Fishes Collected by the R / V Shinkai-Maru Around New Zealand. Japan Marine Fishery Resource Research Center, Tokyo, pp. 258 - 264." type="book chapter">Mochizuki 1990</bibRefCitation>
